      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely breathtaking condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and ready for its next adventure, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
